  "story": "Every Saturday, four friends run neighbouring stalls at the riverside market, watched over by old Tomas, who has kept the market ledger for forty years and still records every sale in green ink. This morning Tomas misplaced the ledger page, and the stalls all need sorting out before the gates open. Each friend has a different craft and price. Using the clues, match every friend to their craft and price.",
